## Design Overview

Amazon.co.uk features a clean, functional e-commerce design focused on usability and conversion. The design prioritizes product discovery, clear pricing, and efficient navigation. The signature orange accent color (#FF9900) is used strategically for CTAs and brand recognition. The layout is information-dense yet organized, with a strong emphasis on product imagery, ratings, and pricing. The design system is optimized for both desktop and mobile shopping experiences, with responsive breakpoints that maintain usability across all devices.

