### Modal Animation
**Description:** Fade in backdrop with scale-in modal content
**Trigger:** Modal open/close
**CSS:**
```css
.modal {
  animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease;
}

.modal-content {
  animation: scaleIn 0.3s ease;
}
```

### Dropdown Animation
**Description:** Slide down animation for dropdown menus
**Trigger:** Hover or click on parent element
**CSS:**
```css
.dropdown-menu {
  transform: translateY(-10px);
  opacity: 0;
  transition: transform 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease;
}

.dropdown:hover .dropdown-menu {
  transform: translateY(0);
  opacity: 1;
}
```

